🍔 Street Bites Franchise Website

A modern, responsive franchise website designed to showcase Street Bites, a fast-growing food brand offering scalable business opportunities across India. The website is built to attract potential franchise partners through strong visuals, clear information, and conversion-focused design.

🚀 Overview

This project presents a complete franchise ecosystem including brand story, investment details, business models, and real success stories. It is designed with a focus on user experience, trust-building, and lead generation.

✨ Features

📌 Hero section with strong call-to-action (Apply for Franchise)
📌 Brand story showcasing growth from local stall to national brand
📌 Franchise models (Food Truck, Takeaway, Full Restaurant)
📌 Investment breakdown with transparent pricing
📌 Step-by-step onboarding process
📌 Profit calculator for ROI estimation
📌 Testimonials & success stories for trust-building
📌 City-wise expansion map
📌 FAQ section for common queries
📌 Fully responsive design

🛠️ Tech Stack

⚡ Next.js (App Router)
🎨 Tailwind CSS / CSS Modules
🧠 JavaScript
📦 PostCSS
(Optional: Tailwind / Bootstrap if used)

🎯 Purpose

To generate franchise leads
To clearly explain business opportunities
To build brand credibility
To simplify decision-making for investors

📊 Key Highlights

💰 Investment Range: ₹8L – ₹35L
📈 ROI Timeline: 18–24 months
🏪 50+ outlets across multiple cities
🤝 500+ happy partners

🧠 Design Approach

Clean and modern UI
Conversion-focused layout
Strong typography & hierarchy
Real-world business storytelling
High visual appeal with food imagery

